<div id= "product-page">
  <div class= "title-bar d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center my-3">
    <div class="text m-0 p-0">
      <h2 class="m-0"><%= @item.name %></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex">
      <% if @item.user == current_user %>
        <%= link_to item_path(@item), data: {turbo_method: :delete, turbo_confirm: "Are you sure?"}, class:"btn-rent" do %>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-trash"></i>
        <%end%>
        <%= link_to edit_item_path, class:"btn-rent" do %>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-pen-to-square"></i>
        <%end%>
        <a href="#" class="btn-rent"><i class="fa-solid fa-share-from-square"></i></a>
      <% else %>
        <a href="#" class="btn-rent"><i class="fa-solid fa-share-from-square"></i></a>
      <%end%>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-photo text-center">
    <div class="row">
      <% @item.photos.each do |photo| %>
        <div class="col-4">
          <%= cl_image_tag photo.key, class:"d-block w-100 m-3", style:"box-shadow: rgba(149, 157, 165, 0.2) 0px 8px 24px;", height: 200, width: 300, crop: :fill %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class= "container-details d-flex justify-content-between">

    <div class="container-info d-flex justify-content-between">

      <div class="item-info">
        <h3>Item's info</h3>
        <p><%= @item.description %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="lessor-info">
        <h3>Lessor's info</h3>
        <p>
        <%# <%= @lessor.info %>
        In pretium condimentum quam, eu pellentesque nisi dictum eu. In id leo ac quam convallis lobortis nec efficitur metus. Maecenas a orci eget felis luctus elementum. Maecenas consectetur ornare erat aliquam molestie. Donec vulputate neque augue, vel malesuada enim pulvinar eu. Duis quis sem justo. Suspendisse a commodo tellus.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="container-book">

      <div class="date">
        <div class="input-date d-flex justify-content-between">
          <div class="begin-date text-center">
            <p class="text">Begin-date</p>
            <p>14/09/2022</p>
          </div>
          <div class="end-date text-center" >
            <p class="text">End-date</p>
            <p>30/09/2022</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="total-date text-center">
          <p class="text">Total days</p>
          <p>16 Days</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn-rent">Book</a>
      </div>

      <div class="price">
        <div class= "daily-price d-flex justify-content-between">
          <p class="text">Daily price:</p>
          <p>$<%= @item.value %></p>
        </div>
        <div class= "days-rented d-flex justify-content-between">
          <p class="text">Days rented for:</p>
          <p><%= 16 %></p>
        </div>
        <div class= "total-price d-flex justify-content-between">
          <p class="text">Total price:</p>
          <p>$<%= 16 * @item.value %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class= container-map>
    <div class="map-div">
      <h3 class="text-center"> Item's Location</h3>
      <div style="width: 100%; height: 400px;"
        data-controller="map"
        data-map-markers-value="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
        data-map-api-key-value="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
